history.content: From my experience, Berkeleytime does not show data is up to date to the minute regarding enrolment, so classes.berkeley.edu and the shopping cart will always have the most updated info.

Hey, I just had a quick question concerning enrollment into CS C8 as a freshman. I was checking my class schedule on Berkeleytime, and it was showing me that discussions are either closed or waitlisted. When I also checked against the academic catalog, I saw that enrollment for discussions is open to freshman, contradicting what information Berkeleytime was showing me. Does anyone have any information regarding this that might clear up my confusion? Thanks a lot in advance.
history.subject: Question about CS C8
